dge cyc-badge2\">⧗</span>` : \"\",\n        receptionsR.some(r=>r.maisA===num||r.maisB===num) ? `<span class=\"extra-badge recep-badge2\">↔</span>` : \"\",\n        m.stations_retro?.length    ? `<span class=\"extra-badge retro-badge\">${m.stations_retro.length} station${m.stations_retro.length>1?\"s\":\"\"}</span>` : \"\",\n        m.fenetre_stellaire?.length   ? `<span class=\"extra-badge\" style=\"color:#5d4037;border-color:#ffb300;background:#fff8e1\">★ ${m.fenetre_stellaire.length}</span>` : \"\",\n        m.eclipse_natal_active?.length ? `<span class=\"extra-badge\" style=\"color:#7c2d12;border-color:#7c2d12\">⚡ Écl.Nat</span>` : \"\",\n        m.lunaisons?.length         ? `<span class=\"extra-badge lunai-badge2\">${m.lunaisons.length} lunaison${m.lunaisons.length>1?\"s\":\"\"}</span>` : \"\",\n        m.eclipses?.length          ? `<span class=\"extra-badge ecl-badge\">⚠ ${m.eclipses.length} éclipse${m.eclipses.length>1?\"s\":\"\"}</span>` : \"\"\n    ].filter(Boolean).join(\"\");\n\n    const s1 = `<div class=\"section-title slow-title\">${L.presenceLentes}</div>\n        ${renderTransits(m.transits_lentes, L.noLente)}`;\n    const s2 = `<div class=\"section-title slow-title\">${L.aspectsLentes}</div>\n        ${renderAspects(m.aspects_lentes, L.noAspLente)}`;\n\n    let s3 = \"\", s4 = \"\";\n    if (showRapides) {\n        s3 = `<div class=\"section-title fast-title\">${L.presenceRapides}</div>\n            ${renderTransits(m.transits_rapides, L.noRapide)}`;\n        s4 = `<div class=\"section-title fast-title\">${L.aspectsRapides}</div>\n            ${renderAspects(m.aspects_rapides, L.noAspRapide)}`;\n    }\n\n    const sAngles    = renderPassagesAngles(m.passages_angles, num);\n    const sStations  = renderStations(m.stations_retro);\n    const sLunai     = renderLunaisons(m.lunaisons);\n    const sEcl       = renderEclipses(m.eclipses);\n    const sFenetresStellair = renderFenetresStellairesTrans(m.fenetre_stellaire);\n    const sEclNatale      = renderEclipseNataleResonance(m.eclipse_natal_active);\n    const sAxe       = renderAxeMaitrises(num);\n    const sRecep     = renderReceptionsMutuelles(num);\n    const sFN        = renderFiguresNatales(num, m.aspects_lentes);\n    const sDig       = renderDignitesActives(m.aspects_lentes);\n    const sTL        = renderTranslationsLumiere(m.translations_lumiere);\n    const sProf      = renderProfection(m.profection);\n    const sIng       = renderIngress(m.ingress);\n    const sCyc       = renderCyclesVie(m.cycles_vie);\n    const sDecl      = renderDeclinaisons(m.declinaisons_texte);\n    const sProg      = renderProgressions(num);\n    const sProgAsp   = renderProgressionAspects(num);\n\n    return `\n    <div class=\"house-block${ANGLE_BY_HOUSE[num] ? \" angular-house\" : \"\"}\">\n        <div class=\"house-banner\">\n            <div class=\"house-title\">${L.maison} ${num}</div>\n            <div class=\"house-meta\">\n                <span class=\"type-badge\" style=\"background:${tc.badge};color:${tc.badgeTxt}\">${labelType}</span>\n                <span class=\"periode-label\">${dateEntreeStr} → ${dateSortieStr}</span>\n                ${extraBadges}\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        ${structureBar}\n        <div class=\"house-content\">\n            ${sEclNatale}${sFenetresStellair}${sProf}${sProg}${sProgAsp}${sCyc}${sAxe}${sRecep}${sEcl}${sLunai}${sAngles}${sStations}${sIng}${sTL}${sDig}${sFN}${sDecl}${s1}${s2}${s3}${s4}\n        </div>\n    </div>`;\n};\n\n// ── Bloc contexte natal avancé (harmonisation avec le rapport Thème) ──\nlet natalAdvancedHTML = '';\nif (dispositorTreeH?.finalDispositors?.length > 0 || accidentalDignityH.length > 0 || hayzPlanetsH.length > 0 || besiegedPlanetsH.length > 0 || moonVOCH) {\n    natalAdvancedHTML = `<div class=\"house-block\" style=\"page-break-before:always;margin-bottom:45px\">\n        <div class=\"house-banner\" style=\"background:${tc.bg}\">\n            <div class=\"house-title\">🔬 ${L.ctxNatal}</div>\n            <div class=\"house-meta\"><span class=\"type-badge\" style=\"background:${tc.badge};color:${tc.badgeTxt}\">${L.techClassiques}</span></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"house-content\">`;\n    if (dispositorTreeH?.finalDispositors?.length > 0) {\n        natalAdvancedHTML += `<div class=\"section-title\" style=\"color:#1e40af;margin-bottom:8px\">${L.arbreDisp}</div>\n            <div style=\"background:#dbeafe;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:0.95rem\">\n            <strong>${L.dispFinaux}</strong> ${dispositorTreeH.finalDispositors.join(', ')}\n            <span style=\"color:#64748b;font-size:0.85em;display:block;margin-top:4px\">${L.dispDesc}</span></div>`;\n    }\n    if (accidentalDignityH.length > 0) {\n        const topRows = accidentalDignityH.slice(0, 5).map((d, i) => {\n            const color = d.score >= 15 ? '#166534' : d.score >= 8 ? '#1e40af' : d.score >= 0 ? '#475569' : '#991b1b';\n            const bg = i % 2 === 0 ? '#fafafa' : '#ffffff';\n            return `<tr style=\"background:${bg}\"><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;font-weight:700\">${glyphs[d.planet]||''} ${d.planet}</td><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;color:${color};font-size:1.05em\">${d.score}</td><td style=\"padding:6px 12px;font-size:0.85em;color:#64748b\">${d.details.join(' · ')}</td></tr>`;\n        }).join('');\n        natalAdvancedHTML += `<div class=\"section-title\" style=\"color:#1e40af;margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:8px\">${L.forcePlan}</div>\n            <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:10px\">\n            <tr style=\"background:${tc.bg};color:white\"><th style=\"padding:7px 12px;text-align:left\">${L.planete}</th><th style=\"padding:7px 12px;text-align:center\">${L.score}</th><th style=\"padding:7px 12px;text-align:left\">${L.detail}</th></tr>\n            ${topRows}</table>`;\n    }\n    if (hayzPlanetsH.length > 0) {\n        natalAdvancedHTML += `<div class=\"section-title\" style=\"color:#2E5FA3;margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:8px\">✦ Hayz</div>` +\n            hayzPlanetsH.map(h => `<div style=\"padding:5px 12px;margin:3px 0;background:#eef2fb;border-left:3px solid #2E5FA3;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.88rem\">${h.description}</div>`).join('');\n    }\n    if (besiegedPlanetsH.length > 0) {\n        natalAdvancedHTML += `<div class=\"section-title\" style=\"color:#dc2626;margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:8px\">⚠ ${L.assiege}</div>` +\n            besiegedPlanetsH.map(b => `<div style=\"padding:5px 12px;margin:3px 0;background:#fef2f2;border-left:3px solid #dc2626;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.88rem\">${b.description}</div>`).join('');\n    }\n    if (moonVOCH) {\n        natalAdvancedHTML += `<div class=\"section-title\" style=\"color:#1F3864;margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:8px\">◯ ${L.luneVOC}</div>\n            <div style=\"padding:5px 12px;background:#e8f0fe;border-left:3px solid #1F3864;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.88rem\">${moonVOCH.description}</div>`;\n    }\n    if (stationaryPlanetsH.length > 0) {\n        natalAdvancedHTML += `<div class=\"section-title\" style=\"color:#2E5FA3;margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:8px\">⏸ ${L.planStation}</div>`;\n        stationaryPlanetsH.forEach(sp => {\n            natalAdvancedHTML += `<div style=\"padding:5px 12px;margin:3px 0;background:#eef2fb;border-left:3px solid #2E5FA3;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.88rem\">\n                <strong>${sp.planet}</strong> — ${sp.direction} ${L.en} ${sp.sign} (M${sp.house}) — ${L.vitesse} ${sp.speed}°/${isEN?'day':'jour'} (${L.seuil} ${sp.threshold}°/${isEN?'day':'jour'}). ${L.energieConc}</div>`;\n        });\n    }\n    natalAdvancedHTML += `</div></div>`;\n}\n\n// ── Forme du thème (Jones) + Signes interceptés ──\nlet chartShapeHTML = '';\nif (chartShapeH.shape || interceptedSignsH.length > 0 || natalStatsH.almutem_figuris) {\n    chartShapeHTML = `<div class=\"house-block\" style=\"margin-bottom:30px\"><div class=\"house-banner\" style=\"background:${tc.bg}\">\n        <div class=\"house-title\">📐 ${L.structTheme}</div>\n        <div class=\"house-meta\"><span class=\"type-badge\" style=\"background:${tc.badge};color:${tc.badgeTxt}\">${L.gouvFormeInt}</span></div>\n    </div><div class=\"house-content\">`;\n    if (natalStatsH.chart_ruler || natalStatsH.almutem_figuris || natalStatsH.sect) {\n        const _csRows = [];\n        if (natalStatsH.chart_ruler) _csRows.push({icon:'♛', label:L.gouverneur, value:natalStatsH.chart_ruler, bg:'#f0fdf4', border:'#16a34a', color:'#14532d'});\n        if (natalStatsH.almutem_figuris) _csRows.push({icon:'⚜', label:'Almutem Figuris', value:natalStatsH.almutem_figuris, bg:'#fef3c7', border:'#d97706', color:'#78350f'});\n        if (natalStatsH.sect) _csRows.push({icon:'☀', label:'Sect', value:natalStatsH.sect, bg:'#fdf2f8', border:'#db2777', color:'#831843'});\n        chartShapeHTML += `<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:16px\">${_csRows.map(r =>\n            `<tr><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;background:${r.bg};border-left:4px solid ${r.border};border-bottom:3px solid white;border-radius:4px;width:50%\"><span style=\"font-size:1.05em\">${r.icon}</span> <strong style=\"color:${r.color}\">${r.label}</strong></td><td style=\"padding:10px 14px;background:${r.bg};border-bottom:3px solid white;font-weight:700;color:${r.color};font-size:1.05em\">${glyphs[r.value]||''} ${r.value}</td></tr>`\n        ).join('')}</table>`;\n    }\n    if (chartShapeH.shape) {\n        chartShapeHTML += `<div style=\"padding:14px 18px;background:#f0f9ff;border-left:4px solid #0284c7;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:12px\">\n            <div style=\"font-weight:700;color:#0369a1;font-size:1.02em;margin-bottom:6px\">🔷 <span style=\"color:#0369a1\">${L.formeTheme}</span> <span style=\"color:#0369a1;font-weight:700\">${chartShapeH.shape}</span></div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:0.9em;color:#475569;line-height:1.5\">${chartShapeH.description || ''}</div></div>`;\n    }\n    if (interceptedSignsH.length > 0) {\n        chartShapeHTML += `<div style=\"padding:14px 18px;background:#e8f0fe;border-left:4px solid #1F3864;border-radius:6px\">\n            <div style=\"font-weight:700;color:#1F3864;font-size:1.02em;margin-bottom:8px\">🔒 ${L.signesInt}</div>\n            ${interceptedSignsH.map(is => `<div style=\"padding:8px 12px;margin-bottom:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);border-radius:4px;border-left:3px solid #7c3aed;font-size:0.9em;color:#3b1f6e;line-height:1.5\">${is.description}</div>`).join('')}</div>`;\n    }\n    chartShapeHTML += `</div></div>`;\n}\n\n// ── Degrés Sabian — SUPPRIMÉ du rapport Prévisions (déjà présent dans le DHN) ──\n\n// ── Profil de sensibilité ──\nlet sensitivityHTML = '';\nif (sensitivityProfileH) {\n    sensitivityHTML = `<div class=\"house-block\" style=\"margin-bottom:30px\"><div class=\"house-banner\" style=\"background:#1F3864\">\n        <div class=\"house-title\">🎯 ${L.sensibilite}</div>\n        <div class=\"house-meta\"><span class=\"type-badge\" style=\"background:#2E5FA3;color:white\">${L.receptTransits}</span></div>\n    </div><div class=\"house-content\">\n        ${sensitivityProfileH.split('\\n').filter(Boolean).map(line => {\n            const isVuln = line.includes('VULNÉRABILITÉ');\n            const isFam = line.includes('FAMILIARITÉ');\n            const bg = isVuln ? '#fef2f2' : isFam ? '#eef2fb' : '#f0f4ff';\n            const border = isVuln ? '#dc2626' : isFam ? '#2E5FA3' : '#1F3864';\n            return `<div style=\"padding:8px 14px;margin:4px 0;background:${bg};border-left:3px solid ${border};border-radius:4px;font-size:0.9rem\">${line}</div>`;\n        }).join('')}\n    </div></div>`;\n}\n\n// ── F2 : HEATMAP D'INTENSITÉ — rendu depuis données centralisées (Analyseur Technique) ──\nconst _renderHeatmap = (hd, bgColor, badgeBg, badgeTxt) => {\n    if (!hd?.grid?.length) return \"\";\n    const grid = hd.grid, labels = hd.colLabels, maxI = hd.maxIntensity || 1;\n    const norm = hd.normalized || [];\n    const top3 = hd.top3 || [];\n    const getHC = (v) => { const r = v / maxI; if (r === 0) return '#f8fafc'; if (r < 0.25) return '#dbeafe'; if (r < 0.5) return '#93c5fd'; if (r < 0.75) return '#3b82f6'; return '#1e40af'; };\n    const getTC = (v) => v / maxI >= 0.5 ? '#fff' : '#1e3a8a';\n    const _nBg = (n) => n >= 75 ? '#1e40af' : n >= 50 ? '#3b82f6' : n >= 25 ? '#93c5fd' : '#dbeafe';\n    const _nTc = (n) => n >= 50 ? '#fff' : '#1e3a8a';\n    let h = `<div class=\"house-block\" style=\"margin-bottom:45px\"><div class=\"house-banner\" style=\"background:${bgColor}\"><div class=\"house-title\">${hd.title}</div><div class=\"house-meta\"><span class=\"type-badge\" style=\"background:${badgeBg};color:${badgeTxt}\">${hd.subtitle}</span>`;\n    if (hd.profLord) h += `<span class=\"type-badge\" style=\"background:#fff8e1;color:#8b6914;margin-left:8px\">♛ ${hd.profLord} (${L.seigneur}) ×1.5</span>`;\n    if (hd.firdMajor) h += `<span class=\"type-badge\" style=\"background:#e8f0fe;color:#1F3864;margin-left:8px\">⏳ ${hd.firdMajor} (${L.firdaria}) ×1.3</span>`;\n    h += `</div></div><div class=\"house-content\">`;\n    const _gr = hd.granularity || \"annual\";\n    const _grFR = {daily:\"pour cette journée\",weekly:\"par jour sur la semaine\",monthly:\"par semaine sur le mois\",annual:\"par mois sur l'année\"};\n    const _grEN = {daily:\"for this day\",weekly:\"per day over the week\",monthly:\"per week over the month\",annual:\"per month over the year\"};\n    const _pedagDT = isEN\n        ? `<strong>💡 How to read this heatmap?</strong><br>This heat map synthesizes the <strong>density of astrological activations</strong> per house ${_grEN[_gr]}. Each cell is a weighted score combining: <strong>planetary weight</strong> (Pluto ×5, Neptune/Uranus/Saturn ×4…), <strong>aspect type</strong> (Conjunction ×1.3, Square/Opposition ×1.2, Trine ×0.8, Sextile ×0.7), <strong>angular house bonus</strong> (Houses 1/4/7/10 ×1.2, cadent ×0.85), and <strong>time-lord amplification</strong> (Annual Lord ×1.5, Firdaria ×1.3). Long transits are <em>distributed</em> over their full duration, repeat passages are reduced (×0.8), and eclipses are capped at 2 per cell. The <strong style=\"color:#991b1b\">Tension</strong> column sums hard aspects (□ ☍ ☌ ⚻), while <strong style=\"color:#1e40af\">Support</strong> sums soft aspects (△ ⚹). <strong>Score</strong> normalizes each house on a 0–100 scale.`\n        : `<strong>💡 Comment lire cette heatmap ?</strong><br>Cette carte thermique synthétise la <strong>densité d'activations astrologiques</strong> par maison ${_grFR[_gr]}. Chaque cellule est un score pondéré combinant : <strong>poids planétaire</strong> (Pluton ×5, Neptune/Uranus/Saturne ×4…), <strong>type d'aspect</strong> (Conjonction ×1.3, Carré/Opposition ×1.2, Trigone ×0.8, Sextile ×0.7), <strong>bonus maisons angulaires</strong> (M1/4/7/10 ×1.2, cadentes ×0.85), et <strong>amplification temporelle</strong> (Seigneur de l'année ×1.5, Firdaria ×1.3). Les transits longs sont <em>distribués</em> sur toute leur durée, les passages multiples (rétrogradation) sont réduits (×0.8), et les éclipses sont plafonnées à 2 par cellule. La colonne <strong style=\"color:#991b1b\">Tension</strong> totalise les aspects durs (□ ☍ ☌ ⚻), tandis que <strong style=\"color:#1e40af\">Support</strong> totalise les aspects doux (△ ⚹). <strong>Score</strong> normalise chaque maison sur une échelle 0-100.`;\n    h += `<div style=\"background:#f0f7ff;border:1px solid #d0daf0;border-radius:8px;padding:14px 18px;margin:0 0 16px;font-size:0.84rem;color:#334155;line-height:1.55\">${_pedagDT}</div>`;\n    h += `<div style=\"overflow-x:auto\"><table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.72rem;text-align:center\"><tr style=\"background:${bgColor};color:white\"><th style=\"padding:4px 4px;text-align:left\">${isEN ? 'House' : 'Maison'}</th>`;\n    labels.forEach(l => { h += `<th style=\"padding:4px 2px\">${l}</th>`; });\